lead_paragraph: Midfielder Pierre-Emile Hojbjerg has urged fans at St Mary's Stadium to help see Southampton through Thursday's tricky Europa League match against Inter Milan, with a win putting the Premier League club in good position to progress to the knockout stages.

headline.print_headline: Hojbjerg Rallies Southampton Fans Ahead of Inter Visit
